This is a WordPress widget to allow WordPress admins to upload or 
select pdf files and then allow clients to download them within the
widget space

Download the latest zip located in the project files and add it within the widget page in Wordpress admin pages

The widget will be available in the appearances>widgets tab

Click the add widget button to the menu sidebar and find downloader widget.

Add it to the sidebar and click on it to change the title and the file location.

They should look the same as the drag and drop ones in the page editor.

v1.1: Removed javascript to enable save button and instead returned an empty string from the form function